1
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:10,080
All our worries.

2
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:17,200
I have a favor to ask of you, Young Marquis.

3
00:01:17,520 --> 00:01:19,640
And you are the only one who can do it.

4
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:22,039
Really?

5
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:23,440
Let's hear it.

6
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:32,020
Why should I help Fang Ji reconcile with his father?

7
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:34,860
Besides, why am I the only one who can do this?

8
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:36,420
Think about it.

9
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:40,200
If Fang Ji makes up with the Prime Minister,

10
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:42,280
then won't he...

11
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:45,410
...stop taking up the Imperial Preceptor's attention?

12
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:49,720
Also, among us,

13
00:01:49,720 --> 00:01:53,000
the only one qualified to sit as an equal with the Prime Minister,

14
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:55,000
and whom the Prime Minister trusts,

15
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:57,640
is our wise and mighty Young Marquis.

16
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:03,160
Stop buttering me up.

17
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:05,400
It's a simple matter, isn't it?

18
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:06,330
I'll handle him.

19
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:17,960
Everyone's here.

20
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:25,320
Let's eat.

21
00:02:27,160 --> 00:02:27,760
Oh my.

22
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:32,340
I just can't figure it out.

23
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:36,240
How was Min Huishi in cahoots with Xiong Renlian?

24
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:40,240
And how did she just die for no reason?

25
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,680
I heard from the jailer...

26
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,680
...it was a ghost.

27
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:47,079
In the blink of an eye,

28
00:02:47,079 --> 00:02:49,160
the body just vanished.

29
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:51,160
You know, some things...

30
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:52,300
This matter...

31
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:52,720
I...

32
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:55,140
Why do you talk so much?

33
00:02:59,280 --> 00:02:59,880
Lord Fang.

34
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:00,360
Yes?

35
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:02,320
Prime Minister Fang.

36
00:03:02,600 --> 00:03:04,680
Didn't we say we'd eat together?

37
00:03:04,920 --> 00:03:05,880
Where is Fang Ji?

38
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,680
He finished eating early.

39
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:08,210
And left.

40
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:14,840
Cousin fell seriously ill while investigating a case earlier.

41
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:16,100
Now he's had a relapse.

42
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,400
He's probably still sleeping.

43
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,760
So he is unwell.

44
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:20,780
That works out.

45
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:22,160
On this trip home,

46
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:24,690
Imperial Physician Hu came along.

47
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:28,380
I'll have Imperial Physician Hu take a look at what's going on.

48
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:30,180
Please, help yourselves.

49
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,200
Let's eat, let's eat.

50
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,079
Yan'er.

51
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:40,480
Eat.

52
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:41,360
Let me tell you,

53
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:43,680
there are some things you just have to believe.

54
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,160
Right?

55
00:03:45,440 --> 00:03:46,000
This is really delicious.

56
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:46,240
Is it good?

57
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:46,900
Delicious.

58
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:59,780
Physician Hu, how is my son's condition?

59
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:12,360
Lord Fang.

60
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:15,490
Please accept my condolences.

61
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,640
Sister, I don't understand.

62
00:04:19,079 --> 00:04:21,040
Why do you cling to Lord Fang,

63
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:23,440
while making eyes at the Young Marquis?

64
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:24,280
Yan'er.

65
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:26,410
What do you mean by that?

66
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,800
If there's nothing going on between you and Lord Fang,

67
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:31,320
why did you rush out after he left last night?

68
00:04:31,400 --> 00:04:32,530
That was because...

69
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:33,360
Because what?

70
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,140
Because...

71
00:04:35,320 --> 00:04:37,720
I was asking Lord Fang to do something for me.

72
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:38,720
Before it's done,

73
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:40,240
I didn't dare make him angry,

74
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,400
for fear he wouldn't help me.

75
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:43,060
He's doing something for you?

76
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:45,040
What does that have to do with me?

77
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:45,940
Sister.

78
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:48,900
Was everything you promised me before a lie?

79
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:50,640
How could I lie to you?

80
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:53,440
Yan'er.

81
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:57,220
Yan'er is the most important person to me right now.

82
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:58,400
Once this is done,

83
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,570
let's go home together.

84
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:07,040
How could this happen?

85
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:10,600
He was alive and kicking yesterday.

86
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:12,280
At this moment...

87
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:16,320
If I, Fang Yu, have committed any sin,

88
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:20,400
Heaven should punish me.

89
00:05:21,280 --> 00:05:24,880
Why torment my poor child?

90
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:30,600
Ji'er.

91
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:31,760
Ji'er.

92
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:33,330
You're still alive.

93
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:35,890
You're still alive.

94
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:38,220
Father.

95
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:40,440
Ji'er.

96
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,600
Actually, I'm fine.

97
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,770
I'm sorry for worrying you.

98
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:50,560
Ji'er, as long as you are safe and sound...

99
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:51,280
Father.

100
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:58,760
I shouldn't have played such a joke.

101
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:02,080
I scared you.

102
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,840
Please punish me.

103
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:06,800
Ji'er.

104
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:10,050
I just want you to be safe and sound.

105
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:12,040
Nothing else matters.

106
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:19,850
Prime Minister.

107
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,360
I was just passing by.

108
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,160
Ji'er.

109
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:33,720
Ji'er.

110
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:36,560
Made up?

111
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:37,440
Yes.

112
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:41,420
We cleared up the misunderstanding.

113
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:43,480
I knew it.

114
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:46,040
Lord Fang was acting

115
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:48,040
like a bitter housewife before.

116
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:52,000
Let this "bitter housewife" take you somewhere nice.

117
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:52,530
Let's go.

118
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:08,280
I let you investigate me.

119
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:10,260
And I made sure you found nothing.

120
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,050
Prime Minister.

121
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:22,840
Lu Shen.

122
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:26,420
Appearing at Xiong Manor in the middle of the night.

123
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:30,440
You really are involved in this case.

124
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:31,800
Kneel down!

125
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:36,020
The Young Marquis is here too.

126
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:40,800
Do you think I need to kneel in my current situation?

127
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:45,120
Since everyone is here today,

128
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:48,560
why don't I tell you an old story?

129
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:51,500
Young Marquis.

130
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:54,920
I bet you'll like it.

131
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:59,920
It's an old story from the Palace twenty years ago.

132
00:08:00,280 --> 00:08:02,000
Back then, it was all because...

133
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:02,860
You bold knave!

134
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,600
Slanderous gossip!

135
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,720
Absolute nonsense!

136
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:06,180
Guards!

137
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:08,280
Gag him!

138
00:08:08,400 --> 00:08:08,930
Yes, sir.

139
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,080
Wait.

140
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,960
Uncle, let him speak.

141
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:17,290
He hasn't finished.

142
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:20,120
How do you know it's nonsense?

143
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:29,920
An ordinary clerk came to the Directorate of Astronomy.

144
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:33,080
He was just a minor official,

145
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:36,559
yet he won His Majesty's favor.

146
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,530
His Majesty said

147
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:40,440
he was a genius.

148
00:08:42,520 --> 00:08:43,600
But everyone said

149
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:45,240
all of this

150
00:08:45,640 --> 00:08:48,320
was because he had a beautiful wife.

151
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,000
Lu Shen.

152
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:53,600
You're at death's door, yet you still dare to slander others?

153
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:56,000
Look at your background.

154
00:08:57,880 --> 00:09:02,010
If the State Preceptor hadn't guided and promoted you to Songfeng Temple,

155
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:04,120
would you be here today?

156
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:05,080
Shut up!

157
00:09:05,680 --> 00:09:07,010
You're no saint either.

158
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:10,520
You and that old charlatan both deserve to die.

159
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:12,020
Young Marquis.

160
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:13,680
To be honest,

161
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:14,580
you might be...

162
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,330
It's witchcraft again.

163
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:29,320
The mastermind...

164
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:31,960
Why do they always silence the suspects so quickly,

165
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:33,690
before we can get a single clue?

166
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:37,040
And they know our every move.

167
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:39,560
Could it be...

168
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:48,880
Oh no.

169
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:53,140
We must protect the officials on the list immediately.

170
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:53,770
Let's go.

171
00:10:09,680 --> 00:10:11,010
I can't take this money.

172
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:13,920
If it weren't for you,

173
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:15,520
and the Gu poison you gave me,

174
00:10:15,640 --> 00:10:19,120
I never could have killed Cao Agou on my own

175
00:10:19,800 --> 00:10:21,730
and taken revenge on those beasts,

176
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,040
let alone escape.

177
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:29,760
I absolutely cannot accept this silver.

178
00:10:36,160 --> 00:10:37,490
After we part ways here,

179
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:40,520
it may be hard to meet again.

180
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:45,290
Please take good care of yourself.

181
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:53,140
We're too late.

182
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:54,640
How did they move so fast?

183
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:04,280
Brother Jian!

184
00:11:04,520 --> 00:11:05,120
Lord Jian!

185
00:11:05,680 --> 00:11:06,540
Stop shouting.

186
00:11:06,800 --> 00:11:07,660
He's over here.

187
00:11:13,800 --> 00:11:14,730
Little Marquis.

188
00:11:18,160 --> 00:11:18,880
Brother Jian.

189
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:19,740
What happened?

190
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:21,960
Luckily, I got here a step ahead of you.

191
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:22,620
Otherwise,

192
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,440
he'd be minced meat by now.

193
00:11:25,040 --> 00:11:27,700
As expected of the Little Marquis. Impressive.

194
00:11:29,160 --> 00:11:29,890
Come with me.

195
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:30,640
Wait.

196
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:34,560
Leave him.

197
00:11:36,400 --> 00:11:37,060
What a joke.

198
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:40,160
I saved him from the blade.

199
00:11:40,680 --> 00:11:42,440
Naturally, I'm taking him.

200
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:46,040
This is a Censorate case.

201
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:48,100
No one dares to interfere.

202
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:53,360
Since you both want Lord Jian,

203
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:55,460
how about this?

204
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,080
I'll find a knife,

205
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:59,960
chop Lord Jian in half,

206
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,840
and you can each have a piece.

207
00:12:03,800 --> 00:12:05,600
Isn't the most important thing right now

208
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:07,560
ensuring Lord Jian's safety?

209
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:10,800
After all, we're on the same side.

210
00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:16,250
What do you mean?

211
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:18,920
Brother Jian and I have long been working together

212
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:21,120
to secretly investigate Lu Shen's crimes.

213
00:12:21,120 --> 00:12:22,560
We were waiting for the right moment

214
00:12:22,560 --> 00:12:23,690
to reveal the truth.

215
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:26,280
We have secret records as proof.

216
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:32,260
If that's the case,

217
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:35,100
why didn't you say so earlier?

218
00:12:36,680 --> 00:12:38,680
Internal secrets of the Censorate

219
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:41,380
cannot be revealed casually.

220
00:12:47,280 --> 00:12:48,810
What did I tell you, Fang Ji?

221
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,560
You're roasting me alive here.

222
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:52,090
I'm almost cooked through.

223
00:12:54,880 --> 00:12:55,480
Watch out!

224
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:57,040
Lord Jian!

225
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:57,920
Gu Lihan!

226
00:13:01,160 --> 00:13:02,560
Miss Gu, are you alright?

227
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:03,420
Miss Gu.

228
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:04,610
How is it?

229
00:13:05,760 --> 00:13:06,490
Are you hurt?

230
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:06,880
Are you okay?

231
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:07,410
I'm fine.

232
00:13:07,760 --> 00:13:08,240
It's okay now.

233
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:08,970
The wound...

234
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:20,340
Luckily, I had this jade pendant.

235
00:13:21,800 --> 00:13:22,330
I'm fine.

236
00:13:30,920 --> 00:13:31,400
Father.

237
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:35,280
Your spirit must be watching over me.

238
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:43,900
It's just a pity to lose such a fine piece of jade.

239
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,060
I'm sorry, Father.

240
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:52,160
A glance at the misty rain, a dream.
